4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science and Machine Learning course that prepares students for careers as AI Machine Learning Engineers. The course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge and can be completed in 16 weeks. Students will learn Python, SQL, Looker, and Streamlit, as well as statistics and industry-standard tools. The curriculum covers topics such as predictive modeling, algorithms, supervised and unsupervised learning models, and developing AI projects. Classes are held three times per week with a maximum of 12 students per class. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. No previous experience is required, and the course is offered in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit the 4Geeks Academy website at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop